Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:52.55,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,孤独が頬を濡らす　濡らすけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:57.59,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,夜明けの気配が静かに満ちて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:02.68,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,私を空へ招くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.02,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,希望が彼方で待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:12.36,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだよ　行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:18.36,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,迷いながらも　君を探す旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:24.70,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,すれ違う意識　手が触れたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:33.13,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,捕まえるよ　しっかり　求め合うココロ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:38.80,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,それは夢の証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:44.34,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,互いを受け止める度に惹かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:49.39,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しい日々はもういらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:54.65,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,互いを受け止めて 生きる喜びに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:03:01.95,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと きっと二人目覚めるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:15.41,OP Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,迷いながらも君を見つけたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:52.55,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,kodoku ga hodo wo nurasu nurasu kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:57.59,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,yoake no kehai ga shizuka ni michite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:02.68,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,watashi wo sore he maneku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.02,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,kibou ga kanata de matteru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:12.36,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,souda yo iku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:18.36,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,mayoi nagara mo kimi wo sagasu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:24.70,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,surechigau ishikite ga fureta yo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:33.13,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,tsukamaeru yo shikkari motomeau kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:38.80,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,sore wa yume no akashi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:44.35,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,tagai wo uketomeru tabi ni hikareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:49.39,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,kanashii hibi wa mou iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:54.65,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,tagai wo uketomete ikiru yorokobi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:03:01.95,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,kitto kitto futari mezameru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:15.41,OP Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,mayoi nagara mo kimi wo mitsuketa yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:52.55,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Como lágrimas de solidão escorrem em minhas bochechas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:57.59,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Eu me surpreendo com o reflexo silencioso do amanhecer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:02.68,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,É um convite para ir em direção ao céu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.02,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Lembrando-me que a esperança reside além dos limites
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:12.36,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Sim, eu irei
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:18.36,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Não importa o quão perdido me sinta, semprei irei lhe dar a mão
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:24.70,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Nossas mãos se encontrarão, mesmo que nossos corações não o façam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:33.13,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Mas agora, irei te abraçar tão forte, que nossos corações irão se entrelaçar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:38.80,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Provando que nosso sonho tornou-se realidade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:44.34,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Sempre que aceitarmos um ao outro, ficaremos mais próximos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:49.39,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Os dias cruéis continuam atrás de nós
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:54.65,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Sempre que aceitarmos um ao outro, poderemos perceber,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:03:01.95,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,perceber como é maravilhoso estarmos vivos
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:15.41,OP English,NTP,0,0,0,,Não importa o quão perdido me sinta, sempre conseguirei te encontrar
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:11.12,ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,静寂さを切り裂くよう　訪れたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:16.79,ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,必然としての邂逅 僕らのために
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:21.67,Alt ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,後悔を嘆く眼に映る君はそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:28.47,Alt ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,憂いを纏って美しく咲いた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:32.64,Alt ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かの生命に溶ける花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:40.77,ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ　君にも見えるだろう きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:47.86,Alt ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,重ねた過ち　塗り替えるよう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:53.45,ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,何度でもいいさ　繰り返してくスタートライン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:59.13,Alt ED Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,過去とは違う明日を　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:04.96,Alt ED Kanji,,0,0,0,,二人だけの希望描くスタートライン
