Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:32.64,Alt ED Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,dareka no seimei ni tokeru hana
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:40.77,ED Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,nee kimi ni mo mieru darou kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:47.86,Alt ED Kanji,NTP,0,0,0,,kasaneta ayamachi nurikaeru you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:53.45,ED Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,nando demo ii sa kurikaeshiteku Startline
